            <fr:title text="Matrix addition and union of relations"><fr:link href="jms-00JO.xml" title="Pointwise addition of matrices" addr="jms-00JO" type="local">Matrix addition</fr:link> and union of <fr:link href="jms-00I7.xml" title="Relation" addr="jms-00I7" type="local">relations</fr:link></fr:title>
            <fr:taxon>Lemma</fr:taxon>
          </fr:frontmatter>
          <fr:mainmatter><html:p>The pointwise sum <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[M\oplus  N]]></fr:tex> of <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[M,N\in \mathrm {Mat}_{\mathbb {B}}{\mathopen {}\left (m,n\right )\mathclose {}}]]></fr:tex> corresponds to the union of the <fr:link href="jms-00IZ.xml" title="The relation associated to a matrix" addr="jms-00IZ" type="local">relations associated</fr:link> to <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[M]]></fr:tex> and <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[N]]></fr:tex>:</html:p><fr:tex display="block"><![CDATA[
 \operatorname {\underline {rel}}_{\mathbb {B}}{\mathopen {}\left (M\oplus  N\right )\mathclose {}} =
 \operatorname {\underline {rel}}_{\mathbb {B}}M \cup  \operatorname {\underline {rel}}_{\mathbb {B}}N
]]></fr:tex><html:p>Moreover, the <fr:link href="jms-00JP.xml" title="The zero matrix" addr="jms-00JP" type="local">zero matrix</fr:link> corresponds to the <fr:link href="jms-00IG.xml" title="The empty relation" addr="jms-00IG" type="local">empty relation</fr:link>: <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\operatorname {\underline {rel}}_{\mathbb {B}}\mathbf {0} = \varnothing ]]></fr:tex>.</html:p>
 
   
